data.name: RT1042.CommandText
data.value: SELECT RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.CUSID, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.PRTNO,rtrim(convert(char(6),RTLessorAVScust.COMQ1)) +'-'+ rtrim(convert(char(6),RTLessorAVScust.lineQ1)) as comqline, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.PRTNO, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.SENDWORKDAT, RTOBJ.CUSNC,CASE WHEN RTOBJ_2.SHORTNC <>'' THEN RTOBJ_2.SHORTNC ELSE RTOBJ_1.CUSNC END,CASE WHEN RTOBJ_4.SHORTNC <>'' THEN RTOBJ_4.SHORTNC ELSE RTOBJ_3.CUSNC END, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.closedat,RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.unclosedat,RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.BONUSCLOSEYM, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.BONUSFINCHK,RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.batchno, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.STOCKCLOSEYM, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.STOCKFINCHK, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.DROPDAT,SUM(CASE WHEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.dropdat IS NULL AND RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY > 0 THEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY ELSE 0 END), SUM(CASE WHEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.dropdat IS NULL AND RCVPRTNO <> '' THEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY ELSE 0 END), SUM(CASE WHEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.dropdat IS NULL AND RCVPRTNO <> '' AND RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.rcvfinishdat IS NOT NULL THEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY ELSE 0 END), SUM(CASE WHEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.dropdat IS NULL AND RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY > 0 THEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.dropdat IS NULL AND RCVPRTNO <> '' AND RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.rcvfinishdat IS NOT NULL THEN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.QTY ELSE 0 END) FROM RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK LEFT OUTER JOIN RTObj RTObj_4 ON RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.REALCONSIGNEE = RTObj_4.CUSID LEFT OUTER JOIN RTEmployee RTEmployee_2 INNER JOIN RTObj RTObj_3 ON RTEmployee_2.CUSID = RTObj_3.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.REALENGINEER = RTEmployee_2.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTObj RTObj_2 ON RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.ASSIGNCONSIGNEE = RTObj_2.CUSID LEFT OUTER JOIN RTEmployee RTEmployee_1 INNER JOIN RTObj RTObj_1 ON RTEmployee_1.CUSID = RTObj_1.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.ASSIGNENGINEER = RTEmployee_1.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTObj INNER JOIN RTEmployee ON RTObj.CUSID = RTEmployee.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.PRTUSR = RTEmployee.EMPLY left outer join RTLessorAVScust on RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.cusid=RTLessorAVScust.cusid LEFT OUTER JOIN RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE ON RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.cusid = RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.CUSID AND RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.PRTNO = RTLessorAVSCustHARDWARE.PRTNO where 1=1 GROUP BY RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.CUSID, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.PRTNO, rtrim(CONVERT(char(6), RTLessorAVScust.COMQ1)) + '-' + rtrim(CONVERT(char(6), RTLessorAVScust.lineQ1)), RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.PRTNO, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.SENDWORKDAT, RTOBJ.CUSNC, CASE WHEN RTOBJ_2.SHORTNC <> '' THEN RTOBJ_2.SHORTNC ELSE RTOBJ_1.CUSNC END, CASE WHEN RTOBJ_4.SHORTNC <> '' THEN RTOBJ_4.SHORTNC ELSE RTOBJ_3.CUSNC END, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.closedat, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.unclosedat, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.BONUSCLOSEYM, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.BONUSFINCHK, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.batchno, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.STOCKCLOSEYM, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.STOCKFINCHK, RTLessorAVSCustSNDWORK.DROPDAT

data.name: RT10422.CommandText
data.value: SELECT RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.PRTNO, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.RCVPRTNO AS RCVPRTNO, RTCODE_1.CODENC, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.APPLYDAT AS APPLYDAT, CASE WHEN RTObj_7.CUSNC='' OR RTObj_7.CUSNC IS NULL THEN RTObj_2.SHORTNC ELSE RTObj_7.CUSNC END AS CUSNC1, CASE WHEN RTObj_1.CUSNC='' OR RTObj_1.CUSNC IS NULL THEN RTObj_3.SHORTNC ELSE RTObj_1.CUSNC END AS CUSNC2, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.CLOSEDAT AS CLOSEDAT, RTObj_4.CUSNC AS CUSNC5, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.CANCELDAT AS CANCELDAT, RTObj_5.CUSNC AS CUSNC6, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.PRTNO AS PRTNO, RTObj_6.CUSNC AS cusnc7,SUM(RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardwareDTL.QTY) AS QTY FROM RTEmployee RTEmployee_4 INNER JOIN RTObj RTObj_6 ON RTEmployee_4.CUSID = RTObj_6.CUSID RIGHT OUTER JOIN RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware ON RTEmployee_4.EMPLY = RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.RCVUSR LEFT OUTER JOIN RTEmployee RTEmployee_3 INNER JOIN RTObj RTObj_5 ON RTEmployee_3.CUSID = RTObj_5.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.CANCELUSR = RTEmployee_3.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTEmployee RTEmployee_2 INNER JOIN RTObj RTObj_4 ON RTEmployee_2.CUSID = RTObj_4.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.CLOSEUSR = RTEmployee_2.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTObj RTObj_3 ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.REALCONSIGNEE = RTObj_3.CUSID LEFT OUTER JOIN RTObj RTObj_2 ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.ASSIGNCONSIGNEE = RTObj_2.CUSID LEFT OUTER JOIN RTEmployee RTEmployee_1 INNER JOIN RTObj RTObj_1 ON RTEmployee_1.CUSID = RTObj_1.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.REALENGINEER = RTEmployee_1.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTObj RTObj_7 INNER JOIN RTEmployee RTEmployee_5 ON RTObj_7.CUSID = RTEmployee_5.CUSID ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.ASSIGNENGINEER = RTEmployee_5.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardwareDTL ON RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.RCVPRTNO=RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardwareDTL.RCVPRTNO left outer join rtcode rtcode_1 on RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.datasrc=rtcode_1.code and rtcode_1.kind='N8' where 1=1 GROUP BY RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.RCVPRTNO , RTCODE_1.CODENC, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.APPLYDAT , CASE WHEN RTObj_7.CUSNC='' OR RTObj_7.CUSNC IS NULL THEN RTObj_2.SHORTNC ELSE RTObj_7.CUSNC END , CASE WHEN RTObj_1.CUSNC='' OR RTObj_1.CUSNC IS NULL THEN RTObj_3.SHORTNC ELSE RTObj_1.CUSNC END, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.CLOSEDAT, RTObj_4.CUSNC, RTObj_5.CUSNC, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.PRTNO, RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardware.CANCELDAT, RTObj_6.CUSNC

data.name: RT104221.CommandText
data.value: SELECT A.RCVPRTNO, A.ENTRYNO, A.PRODNO + '-' + A.ITEMNO AS Expr1, RTProdH.PRODNC, RTProdD1.SPEC, A.QTY, RTCode.CODENC, A.MEMO FROM RTLessorAVSCustRCVHardwareDTL A LEFT OUTER JOIN RTCode ON A.UNIT = RTCode.CODE AND RTCode.KIND = 'B5' LEFT OUTER JOIN RTProdD1 ON A.PRODNO = RTProdD1.PRODNO AND A.ITEMNO = RTProdD1.ITEMNO LEFT OUTER JOIN RTProdH ON A.PRODNO = RTProdH.PRODNO where 1=1 order by A.entryno

data.name: RT10424.CommandText
data.value: SELECT A.CUSID,A.ENTRYNO,A.PRTNO, A.SEQ, RTRIM(CONVERT(CHAR(6),RTLESSORAVSCUST.COMQ1)) +'-'+ RTRIM(CONVERT(CHAR(6),RTLESSORAVSCUST.LINEQ1)) AS COMQLINE, A.PRTNO,A.ENTRYNO,A.CHGDAT, RTCODE.CODENC, RTOBJ.CUSNC, A.SENDWORKDAT, A.DROPDAT, A.DROPDESC, A.CLOSEDAT, A.UNCLOSEDAT, A.BONUSCLOSEYM FROM RTCODE RIGHT OUTER JOIN RTLESSORAVSCUSTCONTSNDWORKLOG A ON RTCODE.CODE = A.CHGCODE AND RTCODE.KIND = 'G2' LEFT OUTER JOIN RTOBJ INNER JOIN RTEMPLOYEE ON RTOBJ.CUSID = RTEMPLOYEE.CUSID ON A.CHGUSR = RTEMPLOYEE.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTLESSORAVSCUST ON A.CUSID=RTLESSORAVSCUST.CUSID WHERE 1=1

data.name: cmd.CommandText
data.value: SELECT A.CUSID,A.ENTRYNO,A.PRTNO, A.SEQ, RTRIM(CONVERT(CHAR(6),RTLESSORAVSCUST.COMQ1)) +'-'+ RTRIM(CONVERT(CHAR(6),RTLESSORAVSCUST.LINEQ1)) AS COMQLINE, A.PRTNO,A.ENTRYNO,A.CHGDAT, RTCODE.CODENC, RTOBJ.CUSNC, A.SENDWORKDAT, A.DROPDAT, A.DROPDESC, A.CLOSEDAT, A.UNCLOSEDAT, A.BONUSCLOSEYM FROM RTCODE RIGHT OUTER JOIN RTLESSORAVSCUSTCONTSNDWORKLOG A ON RTCODE.CODE = A.CHGCODE AND RTCODE.KIND = 'G2' LEFT OUTER JOIN RTOBJ INNER JOIN RTEMPLOYEE ON RTOBJ.CUSID = RTEMPLOYEE.CUSID ON A.CHGUSR = RTEMPLOYEE.EMPLY LEFT OUTER JOIN RTLESSORAVSCUST ON A.CUSID=RTLESSORAVSCUST.CUSID WHERE 1=1
